data.description: Welcome Home! This well cared for home is a 4 Bedroom 2 bath & garage with in-ground pool with covered and screened patio on 1.25 acres.  Roof 2005, New AC installed 2014, new water system, new wood flooring in all bedrooms, 2nd bathroom redone, new pool skimmer, new oven, dishwasher & disposal and stainless steel appliances, Conex Storage Container and new closet systems.  This home is located on a corner lot with pond and dock.  Centrally located near great shopping, restaurants and night life. Don't miss this one!!
data.whatILove: Very well maintained and cared for.  Roof 2005, newer ac, bathroom completely redone.  New water system.  Inground pool and covered and screened patio.  Large Conex storage box included.  Easy access routes to entertainment, restaurants, roadways and airport
